quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  77,41,Those who had guarded (against evil) will be in shades and springs
  77,42,and fruits which they desire
  77,43,"(It will be said), “Eat and drink pleasantly because of that, which you used to do.”"
  77,44,Thus do We reward the doers of good
  77,45,"Sorrowful will be the state on that day, of the deniers"
  77,46,"Eat and enjoy yourselves for a while, you are certainly criminals"
  77,47,"Sorrowful will be the state on that day, of the deniers"
  77,48,"And when it is said to them to bow down, they do not bow down"
  77,49,"Sorrowful will be the state on that day, of the deniers"
  77,50,"Then in which statement after this, will they believe"